race.description: Ladbrokes Mates Mode Pots Max 150 Pts
race.comment: GRETZKY (1) struggled in tougher grade last start after losing his position early at Wentworth Park, but prior to that won comfortably by 3.5 lengths at Wentworth Park (30.11) beating Black Tiara in a Grade 5 on September 12. Ready to return to form. NABIAC MEGS (2) produced a moderate run last time when fifth at this track over 400m behind Full Tilt Tom (23.37) in a Grade 5. In the mix. GONGO GIRL (8) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 5th (19.76) at Muswellbrook. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Better than last start and can bounce back. PANDA UNLEASHED (3) is worth a look over a shorter journey this time.
